---
title: BBQ-Glazed Halloumi & Extra Cheesy Broccoli with Hand-Cut Fries
description: Smokey, sticky BBQ-glazed halloumi meets golden, cheesy broccoli in this flavour-packed feast! Served up with crispy fries for the ultimate crunch, it’s a winning combo of bold, comforting, and totally delicious. Get ready to dig in!

